   [generalinformation.gif]

   Public Information on the Operational Activities of the Authority and
   the District of Columbia Government.

   Department of Employment Services Website
   This web site will make job searches and employer guidance easier and
   faster for the public.

   Office of the Chief Financial Officer
   For information on the City's Annual Budget and Financial Plan.. This
   link will take you to the web site administered by the Chief Financial
   Officer of the District

   Congressional Public Laws and Reports
   Text of Federal Laws that pertain to the Authority and the District
   Government, as well as Authority responses to Congressional mandates
   for reports and information.

   Authority By-Laws
   Description of the operational rules and procedures governing the
   activities of the Authority.

   Internet Resources
   links to sites relating to the District Government, as well as general
   resources on the Web.

